{
  "stem": "444.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we left them, and we came to a place where the-- the-- the employees of the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] city of Warsaw had a kind of convalescent house.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we didn't know it, but at the same house was a hospital for the Polish underground.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't know about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They didn't tell us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But one day-- we found out that one day some German doctors came.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were looking for a place to establish a hospital, and then we find out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They told me to hold up the Germans while they were taking out all the-- the-- in the back, in the woods, the wounded ones.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were there for a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then I became a translator for somebody, for the agriculture inspector.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then, later on, I established my own fruit and vegetable wholesale, which became a large wholesale.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The situation was right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Nobody lived in Warsaw anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But all the agricultural goods were, around Warsaw, still there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was in August, 1944.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was at this time that that woman I told you, the redhead, saw me on the street.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She came running to me, put her arms around me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Finally, she trusted me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I said-- but she still didn't tell me what they were.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Told me that she's over here with her friends, this and this cousin, [INAUDIBLE] nothing was true, and they don't know what to do, if I could help them.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So I said, OK, send them over to me, and I gave them a job loading cabbage-- whatever it was-- because I was selling about 15 car loads of vegetables a day.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We sold 4,000 tons a month.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was the largest-- we employed 117 people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
